🏥 CITY MEDICAL CENTER - PATIENT MANAGEMENT SYSTEM
===================================================

A complete XML-based application for managing patients, appointments, 
and medical records.

📋 FILES INCLUDED:
------------------
1. patients.xml      - Main patient database (XML)
2. style.xsl         - XSLT stylesheet for HTML display
3. clinic.dtd        - Document type definition for validation

🚀 HOW TO RUN:
--------------
Option 1: Using a web browser (simplest)
1. Save all files in the same folder
2. Open patients.xml in any modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge)
3. The XSLT will automatically transform it to HTML

Option 2: Using a local server
1. Install Python: python -m http.server 8000
2. Navigate to http://localhost:8000/patients.xml

Option 3: Using VS Code
1. Install "XML Tools" extension
2. Right-click patients.xml → "Open in Browser"

✨ FEATURES:
-----------
✅ Patient registration and records
