✅ Insurance information
✅ Responsive design
✅ Auto-refresh simulation

🔧 CUSTOMIZATION:
-----------------
Add new patients: Edit patients.xml and add:
<patient id="P004">
  <personal-info>
    <name>New Patient</name>
    <age>XX</age>
    ... etc ...
  </personal-info>
</patient>

Add appointments: Add to <appointments> section

📊 DATA VALIDATION:
-------------------
To validate the XML against DTD:
- Online: https://www.xmlvalidation.com
- Command line: xmllint --valid --noout patients.xml

